what else to do with me.

9
00:01:47,005 --> 00:01:51,772
You mustn't misunderstand about my mother.
She's really a lovely person.

10
00:01:51,943 --> 00:01:56,505
I guess every boy thinks his mother
is beautiful, but my mother really is.

11
00:01:56,681 --> 00:02:01,311
She tells me in every letter she writes how
sorry she is that we're not together more...

12
00:02:01,486 --> 00:02:04,683
...but she has to think of her work.

13
00:02:04,856 --> 00:02:08,815
