She met me in San Francisco once...

14
00:02:08,994 --> 00:02:13,897
...and we were together for two whole
days, just like we were sweethearts.

15
00:02:14,065 --> 00:02:17,899
It was the most wonderful time I ever had.

16
00:02:18,069 --> 00:02:22,563
Then I had to go back
to the military academy.

17
00:02:22,741 --> 00:02:27,041
Every time I walk into that barracks,
I get a kind of...

18
00:02:33,151 --> 00:02:35,381
A kind of a...

19
00:02:40,025 --> 00:02:41,925
I'm sorry.

20
00:02:49,034 --> 00:02:51,901
Kind of a depressed feeling.

21
00:02:52,070 --> 00:02:56,006
