64
00:07:25,610 --> 00:07:28,408
He's not going up
until he checks his knife.

65
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:31,811
We ain't staying long enough for no trouble.
He's just helping a friend.

66
00:07:32,016 --> 00:07:35,383
He's not helping out anyone
unless he checks his knife.

67
00:07:35,553 --> 00:07:39,182
This is the High School for Performing Arts.
We don't cut each other up here.

68
00:07:40,258 --> 00:07:42,021
- You want it?
- I want it.

69
