to learn to dance, anyway?

194
00:21:01,958 --> 00:21:03,653
Yeah, hello?

195
00:21:03,827 --> 00:21:09,322
No, it isn't. This is Naomi Finsecker
speaking. Her mother. Who is this?

196
00:21:19,075 --> 00:21:23,535
Replacement?
What do you mean, replacement?

197
00:21:27,584 --> 00:21:30,280
So is she in or is she out?

198
00:21:33,356 --> 00:21:36,621
I got in! I got in!
I got into Performing Arts!

199
00:21:41,398 --> 00:21:44,060
Doris, we're in!

200
00:22:34,282 --> 00:22:36,944
Get her out of there!

201
00:22:40,221 --> 00:22:44,123
- Hey, later on.
- All right. All right!

202
00:22:44,292 --> 00:22:46,590
See y'all later.

203
00:22:47,362 --> 00:22:50,559
- Hello.
- Hey, mama, get in the car!

204
00:22:54,402 --> 00:22:57,997
Come on, baby, come on.
Don't go to school.

205
00:22:58,173 --> 00:23:01,631
- Martelli, Bruno.
- Bruno. Come on.

206
00:23:01,810 --> 00:23:03,573
Garcia, Raul.

207
00:23:04,879 --> 00:23:08,110
- Garcia, Raul?
- It's Ralph.

208
00:23:09,818 --> 00:23:12,651
- It says Raul.
- I don't relate to that.

209
00:23:13,855 --> 00:23:16,824
- Garcia, Ralph.
- It's Garci.

210
00:23:16,991 --> 00:23:21,052
Ralph Garci. I think they
spelled it wrong on the application.

211
00:23:21,229 --> 00:23:23,789
- Garci, Ralph.
- Here.

212
00:23:26,468 --> 00:23:28,834
- MacNeil, Montgomery.
- Here.

213
00:23:29,404 --> 00:23:32,498
- Monroe, Lisa.
- Yes?

214
00:23:34,008 --> 00:23:35,134
Johnson, Leroy.

215
00:23:37,378 --> 00:23:38,743
Johnson, Leroy?

216
00:23:41,015 --> 00:23:45,952
In future, Mr. Johnson, I'd like you to
leave your ghetto blaster at home, please.

217
00:23:46,354 --> 00:23:49,983
I'd have left it home
if it wasn't so goddamn boring in here.

218
00:23:50,692 --> 00:23:56,597
This is a classroom, Mr. Johnson. You're
going to be here for the next four years...

219
00:23:56,765 --> 00:24:00,223
...with your eyes open,
homework done, pencils sharpened...

220
00:24:00,401 --> 00:24:06,203
...and all food, cigarettes and radios
outside. Do you understand me?

221
00:24:08,109 --> 00:24:11,977
- Why are you here, Mr. Johnson?
